Ray Finch...Kippers or closet kippers! Dire! Are THEY going to resist the rise of the Far Right? No! But will they get elected again if Brexit looks as though it's over? Almost certainly YES! 
Not good. If we are to fight fascism, we need a massive clean out. #EUReform #AntiFa

@eucopresident I voted remain #Remainers, but your tweet clearly illustrates why many of my fellow countrymen voted #Brexit because the EU is run by people like you, and the level of contempt you have for the UK. #EUreform
